author: Ben Marth
title: Monday's Area Scores - October 12
text:
Monday's Area Scores - October 12 - WGEM.com: Quincy News, Weather, Sports, and Radio Member Center: Monday's Area Scores - October 12 Posted: QND fired a team score of 331 to win the Hamilton sectional and earns a trip to this weekend's state tournament. 
**High School Golf, Boys**- Masen Melton: 77, advances to state(Class 2A Lincoln Sectional)- Joe Burke: 78, top Bomber individual - missed qualifying for state by 1 stroke(Class 1A Hamilton Sectional)3) Rock Island Alleman: 358- all 3 teams advance to state-- QND scoresBen Schafer (West Hancock): 85Chase Burk (West Central): 85 **High School Golf, Girls**(Class AA Normal Community Sectional)- Quincy High's Krystal Burgtorf: 87, advances to state(Class A Rochester Sectional)- QND's Haley Haugh (83) and Illini West's Morgan Totsch (90) advance to state**High School Volleyball**
